SUMMARY: PORTLAND WINTER LIGHT FESTIVAL Porch/Light DANCE PARTY with DJ A
 NJALI and the INCREDIBLE KID!
DESCRIPTION:FREE ALL-AGES EVENT!\nPORTLAND WINTER LIGHT FESTIVAL\nPorch/L
 ight Dance Party @ TOC with DJ ANJALI and the INCREDIBLE KID!!\n5-7:30pm 
 | FREE!\n\nDJ Anjali and The Incredible Kid will bring the heat\, invitin
 g kids\, grown-ups\, families\, and friends to dance\, bounce\, and warm 
 up together under the winter lights. Expect a night of motion\, joy\, and
  shared energy\, driven by global beats\, playful movement\, and a strong
  sense of community. Wear your glow gear and be the light show!\n\nCome h
 ungry: local favorite Parking Wok will be on site selling hot\, flavorful
  street food – perfect fuel for dancing and staying cozy all evening. TOC
 ’s bar will be open too\, with Missionary Chocolate Truffles\, Farina coo
 kies\, and beverages for both the over-21 and under-21 crowd.\n\nCheck ou
 t the event on the official PWLF page!\n http://pdxwlf.com/experience/por
 ch-light-2/?eventstart=1770771600&eventend=1770780600&timezone=America%2F
 Los_Angeles\npdxwlf.com/experience/porch-light-2/?eventstart=1770771600&e
 ventend=1770780600&timezone=America%2FLos_Angeles http://pdxwlf.com/exper
 ience/porch-light-2/?eventstart=1770771600&eventend=1770780600&timezone=A
 merica%2FLos_Angeles http://pdxwlf.com/experience/porch-light-2/?eventsta
 rt=1770771600&eventend=1770780600&timezone=America%2FLos_Angeles
