SUMMARY: Portland Winter Light Festival | Porch/Light
DESCRIPTION:TOC is proud to be a part of the Portland Winter Light Festiv
 al. https://pdxwlf.com/ A sequel to last year's "Utopia" the new version 
 for 2026 is "Porch/Light." Connecting with the theme of "All the Little T
 hings\," this existing tree sculpture is enhanced with flickering lightin
 g bugs\, sound by Callie Day\, and projected video elements by microscipi
 st James Weiss.\n\nCreated by J. Sebastian Porter\, James Weiss\, PDX Ros
 e Fabrication\, and Callie Day.
