SUMMARY: TOC & Abbey Arts present Clap Your Hands Say Yeah – Piano & Voic
 e
DESCRIPTION:Doors 6:30pm | All Ages | Bar w/ ID | Tickets $30.50-$55.50\n
 *pricing includes all ticketing fees*\n\nWhile best known for his contrib
 utions to independent rock music with Clap Your Hands Say Yeah over the l
 ast two decades\, few are aware that the piano is the first\, and primary
  compositional\, instrument of Alec Ounsworth.\n\nPiano versions of his s
 ongs have occasionally made appearances on albums\, on bonus tracks\, and
  in live shows. Most recently\, an intimate tour across Europe has been s
 old out\, complemented by a 10” and select tracks available on digital pl
 atforms. With more Piano & Voice shows to come\, a very limited bootleg r
 ecording from the three-night residency at London’s Servant Jazz Quarters
  will be available on vinyl exclusively during the tour.\n\nThese piano a
 nd voice versions showcase the depth and resolute character of CYHSY’s re
 pertoire in its purest form.
