SUMMARY: An Evening with Väsen
DESCRIPTION:Doors at 6:30pm | All Ages | Bar w/ ID | Tickets ADV $29.50 /
  DOS $34.50\n*Pricing Includes all ticketing fees*\n\nVäsen-Duo\, Mikael 
 Marin and Olov Johansson have\, after 37 years of interaction and touring
 \, refined their sound and their stage presence to the extent that today 
 they are unique in their kind. With their playful and perfect interplay\,
  they seem to defy the laws of physics in what appears to be a telepathic
  communication.
