SUMMARY: Concert Mosaic
DESCRIPTION:Doors at 6:00pm | All Ages | Bar w/ ID | Tickets $27 General 
 Admission ($30 at the door) | $18 Cascadia Members\, Seniors\, Military\,
  Working Artists ($20 at the door) | $9 Students ($10 at the door) | $10 
 Livestream Only\n\nFor International Women’s Day 2026\, we celebrate the 
 creative and collaborative spirit of women artists from Oregon and Washin
 gton. Experience powerful new works by Northwest women composers\, brough
 t to life by acclaimed performers Julia Lee (piano)\, Diane Chaplin (cell
 o)\, and Tatiana Kolchanova (violin) — set against a backdrop of original
  visual art created in collaboration with each musical piece. Curated by 
 Dianne Davies\, Lisa Marsh\, and Linda Woody\, this concert honors the vo
 ices and visions of Northwest women through their vivid blend of sound an
 d imagery
