SUMMARY: FREE Lunchtime Concert: Sharon Fendrich & Stephanie Torres De Lo
 s Santos w/ Theresa Koon
DESCRIPTION:TOC presents Lunchtime FREE Concerts every FIRST and THIRD We
 dnesday of the month. Our gift to the community for over 56 years\, join 
 us in person or on our Youtube Channel. https://www.youtube.com/channel/U
 CLiO4ZclyOFIe8HiOFzWJyg\n\nSharon Fendrich & Stephanie Torres De Los Sant
 os perform The Human Condition in Song: The Music of Kurt Weill and Jacqu
 es Brel. With Theresa Koon on piano.\n\nStephanie Torres De Los Santos an
 d Sharon Fendrich unite cabaret\, musical theater\, and classical voice. 
 Kurt Weill & Jacques Brel: The Human Condition in Song draws on the visce
 ral intensity of singer/songwriter Jacques Brel and the genre-bending pow
 er of Kurt Weill. Stephanie’s character-driven storytelling meets Sharon’
 s expressive operatic soprano in a vocally diverse exploration of love\, 
 rage\, reflection\, and resilience. Their provocative and socially aware 
 repertoire is strikingly relevant today. https://sharonfendrich.com/home\
 n\nsharonfendrich.com/home https://sharonfendrich.com/home\n\nWATCH THE L
 IVESTREAM https://youtube.com/live/LDob4x_ApZc\n\n
