 rs\, theater-lovers\, bar-mongers and pretty much anyone who wanders publ
 ic spaces in Portland have stories about encountering Brazilian duo Johnn
 y Franco & his real brother Dom - they played 374 shows in 2025.\n\nFrida
 y\, March 20th\, marks their debut performance at The Old Church.\nIt's t
 heir most straight-forward program of the past four years featuring crowd
 -favorite numbers from their vast repertoire of covers and originals as w
 ell as 30 minutes of new music. A show dedicated to celebrate the release
  of the upcoming EP 'At Bens Garage' out on all streaming platforms the s
 ame day.
