SUMMARY: FREE Lunchtime Concert: Troy Rulmyl & Josh O'Renick
DESCRIPTION:TOC presents Lunchtime FREE Concerts every FIRST and THIRD We
 dnesday of the month. Our gift to the community for over 56 years\, join 
 us in person or on our Youtube Channel. https://www.youtube.com/channel/U
 CLiO4ZclyOFIe8HiOFzWJyg\n\nTroy Rulmyr and Josh O'Renick of Ghosts in the
  Clover.\n\nTroy and Josh will tell stories and sing songs from the compl
 eling past of Ireland\, weaving culture\, heritage\, and song seamlessly 
 to create an intimate show for the storied TOC Lunchtime concert series!\
 n\nGhosts in the Clover is a rebel-folk band rooted in the fight for the 
 marginalized\, the silenced\, and the disavowed. Their songs are shaped b
 y loss\, resistance\, exile\, and perseverance. They write music inspired
  by historical trauma\, conflict\, displacement\, and unresolved narrativ
 es.\n\nghostsintheclover.com/ https://ghostsintheclover.com/\n\n\nWATCH T
 HE LIVESTREAM https://youtube.com/live/IC5nT660rZM
